name: Zig zag wino shoes winos
description:
Zig-Zag footwear has been the original "Wino" low top oxford in the California Lifestyle scene since 1970's easy to wear, super comfortable and inexpensive too.
These shoes are actually hard to find so go ahead and order both colors ! We have them in Vegas! Available in most sizes, these shoes are loved by all kinds of people from surfers, gangsters, to rockabilly and skaters get yours today

* when ordering use your converse chucks as a guide , zig zags run big. Usually the same size you wear in converse will be the same size for your zig zags include the size you need in order details please
